Results
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In this section we present results of the field experiment.
 We first look at cooperative decision making and then look at equity in
 time use.
 We then turn to decision making with respect to investment and look at
 the impact on household level outcomes.
 In a final subsection we look if the intervention also had an impact on
 how spouses deal with disagreement.
\end_layout

