 video as a couple as compared to within households where only one of the
 spouses was shown the video, but also here the difference is not significant.
 There are indications that timely weeding was less common among households
 where the couple was shown the video, but the difference is not significant.
 Also here, we do not find any significant impact of the second treatment.
\end_layout

